#

Avocado and Black Bean Guacamole

10 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeLow-Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerSnackHealthy

Description

A creamy and nutritious dip combining the richness of avocados with the heartiness of black beans, perfect for any gathering!

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • canned black beans: 1 can (15 oz)
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh cilantro: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • red onion: 1 small, diced
  • tomato: 1 medium, diced
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
